==社会和文化==
对氯间二甲苯酚溶液有多种品牌名称，例如[[滴露|滴露]]。滴露消毒液含 4.8% 对氯间二甲苯酚，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mhra.gov.uk/home/groups/spcpil/documents/spcpil/con1412920124477.pdf |title=Summary of Product Characteristics / Dettol Liquid |date=22 November 2010 |publisher=MHRA |accessdate=9 November 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20150108224624/http%3A//www.mhra.gov.uk/home/groups/spcpil/documents/spcpil/con1412920124477.pdf |archivedate=2015-01-08 |df= }}</ref>其余为作为溶剂的[[松节油|松节油]]、[[异丙醇|异丙醇]]、[[蓖麻油|蓖麻油]]、皂基和水。向滴露溶液加水会得到白色的乳浊液。

